Quirk yang bernama Blackwhip itu.

124
00:07:58,950 --> 00:08:00,910
Membosankan.

125
00:08:00,910 --> 00:08:03,290
Tidak ada artinya jika tak bisa digunakan.

126
00:08:03,290 --> 00:08:04,540
Aku pulang dulu.

127
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:08,580
Rasanya kesal sekali melihatmu
sibuk bergumam di sana.

128
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:12,790
Hari ini sampai sini saja.

129
00:08:12,790 --> 00:08:14,120
Baiklah.

130
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:23,620
Apa ini kekuatan All For One?

131
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:26,790
Keparat.

132
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:30,620
"TETSUTETSU TETSUTETSU, QUIRK: STEEL"
Hei, jangan terus bicara kotor.

133
00:08:30,620 --> 00:08:32,950
"EIJIRO KIRISHIMA, QUIRK HARDENING"
Tapi, aku yang hari ini

