184
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,950
Midoriya, Togata.

185
00:11:23,950 --> 00:11:25,700
Maaf memanggil kalian keluar.

186
00:11:25,700 --> 00:11:28,080
Aku butuh bantuan Monoma.

187
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:32,500
Sangat disayangkan Eri dan Monoma
tidak cocok dalam aspek psikologi.

188
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:35,410
Kau menganggapku sebagai apa?

189
00:11:47,790 --> 00:11:49,700
Bagaimana, Monoma?

190
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:52,620
Ini "peluru kosong".

191
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:56,870
Maaf, aku telah mengecewakanmu.

192
00:11:56,870 --> 00:11:58,950
Benarkah? Sungguh disayangkan.

193
00:11:58,950 --> 00:12:01,450
Menduplikasi Quirk Eri...

194
00:12:01,450 --> 00:12:03,040
Apa yang ingin dia lakukan?

195
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:05,040
Monoma, apa itu "peluru kosong"?

196
